  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Taffy</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Taffy</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">food</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Items\" title=\"Items\">item</a> made by adding 3.0 units of <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweetener\" title=\"Sweetener\">Sweetener</a>. It takes 40 seconds to cook.\n</p><p>Adding any <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meats</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Nuggets\" title=\"Honey Nuggets\">Honey Nuggets</a>, unless 3 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honeycomb\" title=\"Honeycomb\">Honeycombs</a> are used, which will then result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meatballs\" title=\"Meatballs\">Meatballs</a>. Adding 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pumpkin\" title=\"Pumpkin\">Pumpkin</a> may result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pumpkin_Cookies\" title=\"Pumpkin Cookies\">Pumpkin Cookies</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prerequisites\">Prerequisites</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweetener\" title=\"Sweetener\"><img alt=\"Sweetener.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sweetener.png?4c4870\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" title=\"Meats\"><img alt=\"Meats Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Meats_Crock_Pot.png?bb1767\" width=\"580\" height=\"108\"></a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweetener\" title=\"Sweetener\"><img alt=\"Sweetener.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sweetener.png?4c4870\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3.0</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Taffy\" title=\"Taffy\"><img alt=\"Taffy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Taffy.png?e84907\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\">Examples</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\"><img alt=\"Honey.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey.png?d057e9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Taffy\" title=\"Taffy\"><img alt=\"Taffy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Taffy.png?e84907\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Prototype\" title=\"Prototype\"><img alt=\"Prototype.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Prototype.png/24px-Prototype.png?689878\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a> A recipe for taffy that extenuates as much hunger value as possible.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\"><img alt=\"Honey.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey.png?d057e9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\"><img alt=\"Honey.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey.png?d057e9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Taffy\" title=\"Taffy\"><img alt=\"Taffy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Taffy.png?e84907\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honeycomb\" title=\"Honeycomb\"><img alt=\"Honeycomb.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honeycomb.png?56b468\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berry\" title=\"Berry\"><img alt=\"Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Berry.png?ddd757\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Taffy\" title=\"Taffy\"><img alt=\"Taffy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Taffy.png?e84907\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweetener\" title=\"Sweetener\"><img alt=\"Sweetener.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sweetener.png?4c4870\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake\" title=\"Mandrake\"><img alt=\"Mandrake.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Mandrake.png?c94a2f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Taffy\" title=\"Taffy\"><img alt=\"Taffy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Taffy.png?e84907\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>50% chance to result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake_Soup\" title=\"Mandrake Soup\">Mandrake Soup</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweetener\" title=\"Sweetener\"><img alt=\"Sweetener.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sweetener.png?4c4870\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pumpkins\" title=\"Pumpkins\"><img alt=\"Pumpkins.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pumpkins.png?81d566\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Taffy\" title=\"Taffy\"><img alt=\"Taffy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Taffy.png?e84907\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>50% chance to result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pumpkin_Cookies\" title=\"Pumpkin Cookies\">Pumpkin Cookies</a>.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\"><img alt=\"Honey.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey.png?d057e9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Taffy\" title=\"Taffy\"><img alt=\"Taffy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Taffy.png?e84907\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/64px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Taffy\" title=\"Taffy\"><img alt=\"Taffy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Taffy.png?e84907\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pig_Icon\" title=\"Pig Icon\"><img alt=\"Pig Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Pig_Icon.png/42px-Pig_Icon.png?2561d3\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Manure\" title=\"Manure\"><img alt=\"Manure.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Manure.png?f3cf48\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tips\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Prototype\" title=\"Prototype\"><img alt=\"Prototype.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Prototype.png/32px-Prototype.png?689878\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> Tips</span></h2>\n<ul><li>For players who have a reliable source of <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a>, Taffy can be a viable method for boosting <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sanity\" title=\"Sanity\">Sanity</a>, as the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Health\" title=\"Health\">Health</a> penalty from it can be negated by eating a Honey. With 3 Honey and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twigs</a>, the player can restore a total of 0 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Health\" title=\"Health\"><img alt=\"Health Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Health_Icon.png/20px-Health_Icon.png?1ec0e6\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a>, 34 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hunger\" title=\"Hunger\"><img alt=\"Hunger Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hunger_Icon.png/20px-Hunger_Icon.png?9d0486\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a>, and 15 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sanity\" title=\"Sanity\"><img alt=\"Sanity Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Sanity_Icon.png/20px-Sanity_Icon.png?eae728\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a> in this way.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Taffy was added in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve/Version_History#Insanity!\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve/Version History\">Insanity!</a></i> update.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Insanity!.jpg\" class=\"image\" title=\"Taffy as seen in the poster for the Insanity! update.\"><img alt=\"Taffy as seen in the poster for the Insanity! update.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Insanity%21.jpg/65px-Insanity%21.jpg?45f5fe\" width=\"65\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Taffy as seen in the poster for the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve/Version_History#February_12,_2013_–_Insanity!\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve/Version History\">Insanity!</a></i> update.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:CD_taffy.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\"><img alt=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/CD_taffy.png/120px-CD_taffy.png?180424\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/CD_Don%27t_Starve\" title=\"CD Don&#x27;t Starve\">CD Don&#x27;t Starve</a>.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Taffy_128x128.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\"><img alt=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Taffy_128x128.png/120px-Taffy_128x128.png?fbd554\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Taffy#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Taffy#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
