  "plainText": "Don't Starve\nTogether\nTaffy\nFood Info\n25\n-3\n15\nGoodies\nObject Info\n15 Days\nCan be Burned\n40\nCooking Info\nx3 x1\n40 sec\n10\nMiscellaneous\n\"taffy\"\n“My dentist'd get mad if I ate this... but I don't have one.”\n–Wilson\n“Sugary things burn great, but I should eat this instead.”\n–Willow\n“Is taffy for crushing!”\n–Wolfgang\n“Never imagined I could make a thing so sweet.”\n–Wendy\n“STICKY AND SWEET. LOW NUTRITIONAL VALUE DETECTED.”\n–WX-78\n“I don't much care for sweets, but... desperate times.”\n–Wickerbottom\n“Sugary. Good.”\n–Woodie\n“It's almost entirely sugar.”\n–Maxwell\n“Comprised mostly of honey. But I am not complaining.”\n–Wagstaff\n“Löng will the saga öf this taffy be töld.”\n–Wigfrid\n“Candy!”\n–Webber\n“Maybe I could wax my board with this stuff.”\n–Walani\n“I hope it never dislodges from my teeth!”\n–Warly\n“Sticks ta me no teeth.”\n–Woodlegs\n“IS'T CANDY O' STICKINESS!”\n–Wilba\n“Chewy goo”\n–Wormwood\n“Bite sized tooth decay.”\n–Wheeler\nTaffy is a Crock Pot food item made by adding 3.0 units of Sweetener. It takes 40 seconds to cook.\nAdding any Meats will result in Honey Nuggets, unless 3 Honeycombs are used, which will then result in Meatballs. Adding 1 Pumpkin may result in Pumpkin Cookies.\nPrerequisites[edit | edit source]\nRequires:\nExcludes:\nRecipe[edit | edit source]\n×3.0\nExamples[edit | edit source]\n×3\nA recipe for taffy that extenuates as much hunger value as possible.\n×3\n×3\n×3\n50% chance to result in Mandrake Soup\n×3\n50% chance to result in Pumpkin Cookies.\n×3\nUsage[edit | edit source]\nTips[edit | edit source]\nFor players who have a reliable source of Honey, Taffy can be a viable method for boosting Sanity, as the Health penalty from it can be negated by eating a Honey. With 3 Honey and Twigs, the player can restore a total of 0 , 34 , and 15 in this way.\nTrivia[edit | edit source]\nTaffy was added in the Insanity! update.\nGallery[edit | edit source]\nTaffy as seen in the poster for the Insanity! update.\nOriginal HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don't Starve.\nIcon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\nBy TypeBy Crock Pot Value\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Type)\nVeggie\nSeeds\nMeat\nGoodies\nGeneric\nHorrible\nRoughage\nElementals\nBurnt\nRaw\nGears\nGold Dust\nBerry\nWood\nNitre\nLunar Shards\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Value)\nMeats\nFishes\nVegetables\nFruits\nMonster Food\nEggs\nDairy\nSweetener\nFrozen\nInedibles\nMagic\nFat\nSeed\nJellyfish\nBone\nFilter\nAntihistamine\nDecoration\nBug\nNo Value Food",
