  "wikitext": "{{Navbutton/Separation}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|icon = Taffy.png\n|image = Taffy Dropped.png\n|foodRecipe ={{Pic|32px|Sweetener}}x3 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x1\n|foodType =[[Goodies]] [[File:Goodies.png|32px|link=Goodies]]\n|stack          = 40\n|canBeBurned=1\n|spoil          = 15 Days\n|hpRestored     = -3\n|hungerRestored = 25\n|sanityRestored = 15\n|cooktime       = 40 sec\n|priority       = 10\n|spawnCode      = \"taffy\"\n}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = My dentist'd get mad if I ate this... but I don't have one.\n|willow = Sugary things burn great, but I should eat this instead.\n|wolfgang = Is taffy for crushing!\n|wendy = Never imagined I could make a thing so sweet.\n|wx78 = STICKY AND SWEET. LOW NUTRITIONAL VALUE DETECTED.\n|wickerbottom = I don't much care for sweets, but... desperate times.\n|woodie = Sugary. Good.\n|maxwell = It's almost entirely sugar.\n|wagstaff = Comprised mostly of honey. But I am not complaining.\n|wigfrid = Löng will the saga öf this taffy be töld.\n|webber = Candy!\n|walani = Maybe I could wax my board with this stuff.\n|warly = I hope it never dislodges from my teeth!\n|woodlegs = Sticks ta me no teeth.\n|wilba = IS'T CANDY O' STICKINESS!\n|wormwood = Chewy goo\n|wheeler = Bite sized tooth decay.\n|choose = webber\n}}\n\n'''Taffy''' is a [[Crock Pot]] [[food]] [[items|item]] made by adding 3.0 units of [[Sweetener]]. It takes 40 seconds to cook.\n\nAdding any [[Meats]] will result in [[Honey Nuggets]], unless 3 [[Honeycomb]]s are used, which will then result in [[Meatballs]]. Adding 1 [[Pumpkin]] may result in [[Pumpkin Cookies]].\n\n== Prerequisites ==\n* Requires: [[File:Sweetener.png|link=Sweetener]]\n* Excludes: [[File:Meats Crock Pot.png|link=Meats]]\n\n== {{pic|32|Cookbook}} Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Sweetener\n|comparator1 = &times;\n|count1 = 3.0\n|item2 = Filler\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Taffy\n}}\n\n== Examples ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Honey\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Twigs\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Taffy\n|note={{Pic24|Prototype}} A recipe for taffy that extenuates as much hunger value as possible.}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Honey\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Honey\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Taffy\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Honeycomb\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Berry\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Taffy\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Sweetener\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Mandrake\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Taffy\n|note = 50% chance to result in [[Mandrake Soup]]\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Sweetener\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Pumpkins\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Taffy\n|note = 50% chance to result in [[Pumpkin Cookies]].\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Honey\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Ice\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Taffy\n|dlc = Reign of Giants\n}}\n== {{pic|32|Icon Tools}} Usage ==\n{{Recipe\n|item = Taffy\n|tool = Pig Icon\n|result = Manure\n}}\n== {{pic|32|Prototype}} Tips==\n* For players who have a reliable source of [[Honey]], Taffy can be a viable method for boosting [[Sanity]], as the [[Health]] penalty from it can be negated by eating a Honey. With 3 Honey and [[Twigs]], the player can restore a total of 0 {{Hp}}, 34 {{Hunger}}, and 15 {{Sanity}} in this way.\n\n=={{pic|32|Placeholder}} Trivia ==\n* Taffy was added in the ''[[Don't Starve/Version History#Insanity!|Insanity!]]'' update.\n\n== {{pic32|Blueprint}} Gallery ==\n<gallery captionalign=\"center\" hideaddbutton=\"true\">\nInsanity!.jpg|Taffy as seen in the poster for the ''[[Don't Starve/Version History#February 12, 2013 – Insanity!|Insanity!]]'' update.\nCD taffy.png|Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from [[CD Don't Starve]].\nTaffy 128x128.png|Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\n</gallery>\n{{Crock Pot Food}}\n__NOTOC__\n[[ru:Ириска]]\n[[fr:Bonbon]]\n[[vi:Taffy]]\n[[Category:Crock Pot Recipes]]\n[[Category:Flammable Objects]]\n[[Category:Perishables]]\n[[Category:Sanity Boost]]\n[[Category:Health Loss]]"
